  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">&quot;This grant will support NRDC&#x2019;s growing clean energy programs in China. In China, NRDC is leading the effort to cap new coal capacity. The organization is also advancing reforms in the power sector to promote low-carbon electricity, efficient appliances, and reduced F-gases. The program&#x2019;s priorities for 2019 are to advance policy that will address air pollution through a transition from coal-based boilers to efficient electric air and ground source heat pumps. &quot;</narrative>
